唐尼将自己的宗教信仰描述为[[犹太佛教徒|犹太佛教徒]]<ref name="JewishBuddhist">{{Cite web |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/21/arts/music/robert-downey-jr-the-album.html?mtrref=en.wikipedia.org&gwh=A9553E3871257B3E208A65784235AA02&gwt=pay |title = Robert Downey Jr.: The Album |date = 2004-11-21 |publisher = The New York Times |language = en |access-date = 2018-04-21 |archive-date = 2019-05-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190519182214/https://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/21/arts/music/robert-downey-jr-the-album.html?mtrref=en.wikipedia.org&gwh=A9553E3871257B3E208A65784235AA02&gwt=pay |dead-url = no }}</ref>，而且研究[[占星術|占星術]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/english/hollywood/news/Celebs-seek-guidance-from-the-stars/articleshow/12731100.cms |title = Celebs seek guidance from the stars |author = Anjali Muthanna |date = 2012-04-20 |publisher = The Times of India |language = en |access-date = 2018-04-21 |archive-date = 2020-11-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201119012426/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/english/hollywood/news/Celebs-seek-guidance-from-the-stars/articleshow/12731100.cms |dead-url = no }}</ref>。過去，唐尼一直對[[基督教|基督教]]和[[國際奎師那知覺協會|哈瑞奎師那]]運動感興趣<ref name="JewishBuddhist" />。

